hoursOfOperation.remarks:
Military activities:
To be activated by NOTAM during specific state functions. Nairobi JKIA and Nairobi Wilson will be closed during such exercises. (Uhuru park, Nyayo stadium and Jamuhuri park)

properties.name: HKD13
properties.remarks:
Military Flying Training Area
Control of the area will be exercised by Eastleigh TWR on FREQ 124.3 MHZ.
Note: aircraft equipped with FREQ 124.3 MHZ may be permitted to fly through the area provided that the pilot :-
i)Maintain flight under VFR.
ii) there is radio contact 5 minutes before entering the area.
iii) The flight adheres to TWR restriction.
Departing aircraft should obtain
clearance
from Eastleigh TWR
